description: Charming, light filled, spacious condo in the highly desirable Hunter's Branch community!   Walk to Metro   Underground Parking Space   Spacious Rooms   Open Floor Plan   Lots of kitchen counter space and storage   Balcony   High ceilings   Ample visitor parking and room for second vehicle.  Full size laundry - washer/dryer set in unit. Cozy gas fireplace in large main living area, plenty of room for relaxing, entertaining, and gathering. Easy commuting, Close to 495, 66,  Rt 29, Rt 50; Mosaic District, Pan Am Shopping Center, Nottoway Park, Tysons Corner, Oak Marr Golf Center, and Downtown Vienna, all just a short distance away. Highly rated Oakton High School pyramid.
